com.tinkerpop.blueprints.oupls.sail.pg

Class PropertyGraphSail

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tinkerpop.blueprints.oupls.sail.pg.PropertyGraphSail
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.openrdf.sail.Sail

    public class PropertyGraphSail
extends Object
implements org.openrdf.sail.Sail
    A Sail implementation which provides an RDF view of any Blueprints graph. PropertyGraphSail can be configured to provide one of two kinds of views: one in which edges are first-class objects, with edge ids, types, labels, heads, and tails each modeled as statements, and another in which each edge is a single statement.
    Author:
    Joshua Shinavier (http://fortytwo.net)
